data.description: OFFERING $15k in SELLER CREDITS! Welcome to a beautiful, gated community centrally located from major highways, Theme Parks, Restaurants, & Shops! This Spacious 5 Bed/3 Bath  Office+Large Loft home has the Beauty & upgrades you were looking for! Beautiful wood plank-style tile floors, tall ceilings, and lots of natural lighting. Kitchen is upgraded with granite countertops, large cabinets, Stainless steel appliances, and a large pantry. The kitchen opens to the living and dining area which oversees the backyard oasis! A guest bed+full bath is conveniently located downstairs! The upper floor features the remainder of the guest bedrooms, Loft, Laundry & Master Suite that will not disappoint! Home is fully covered with a water filtration system and Taexx Pest control system that targets the pests inside the walls! AC Nitrogen added & recently serviced. Amenities include a community pool & cabana, fitness center, dog park, playground and a community dock & boat slips providing Lake access
